  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to compare the effectiveness of topical tacrolimus,
      triamcinolone and placebo in alleviating signs and symptoms of oral lichen planus (OLP).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <overall_status>Terminated</overall_status>
  <why_stopped>
    Lack of resources
  </why_stopped>
